DISCLAIMER:
===========

The original computational engines and tools (EDAC by Garcia de Abajo, and 
Multiplet/cluster/visualization tools by Professor Krüger) are the intellectual
property of their respective authors. This license applies specifically to 
the GUI interface, integration work, Linux compatibility improvements, and 
documentation created by TeslaYet.

Users should respect the original authors' work and cite appropriate publications
when using the computational engines for academic research.

For questions about licensing of the original computational engines, please
contact the original authors or institutions. 